text: Andrey Anatolyevich Shumilin (; 9 March 1970 – 8 June 2022) was a Russian wrestler. He competed in the 1996 Summer Olympics and came fourth. Shumilin died on 8 June 2022 at a hospital in Berlin, Germany from cancer, aged 52.В Германии умер депутат из Калининграда Андрей Шумилин ==References== Category:1970 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Olympians for Russia Category:Russian wrestlers Category:Cancer deaths in Germany
